svg.title: Architecture Overview Diagram Template (Neon Cyber AI Style)
svg.desc:
This SVG file serves as a template for architecture overview diagrams in a "Neon Cyber AI" style. Expected elements: - **Color Palette**: Dark background (e.g., deep blues, purples, blacks) with vibrant, glowing neon accents (e.g., electric blues, bright greens, fuchsia, cyber yellow). - **Shapes**: Geometric shapes (rectangles, circles, triangles) with sharp edges or subtle glows. Rounded corners should be minimal. - **Lines**: Thin, glowing lines to connect components, possibly animated or dashed for data flow. - **Text**: Sans-serif, futuristic fonts (e.g., a monospaced or slightly glitchy font) in neon colors. - **Icons**: Minimalist, abstract, or circuit-board-like icons for different modules (Isaac Sim, Isaac ROS, Nav2). - **Effects**: Subtle gradient fills, inner/outer glows, scanline/glitch effects, binary code patterns in the background. - **Overall Feel**: High-tech, futuristic, slightly abstract, emphasizing data and AI processing.
This diagram should visually represent the high-level architecture of the AI-Robot Brain module, showing the main components (Isaac Sim, Isaac ROS, Nav2, Robot Hardware/Physical AI), their interactions, and data flow.
